=head1 DESCRIPTION

A summary of the resource scan. This is returned by the
C<ListResourceScan> API action.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 EndTime => Str

The time that the resource scan was finished.


=head2 PercentageCompleted => Num

The percentage of the resource scan that has been completed.


=head2 ResourceScanId => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource scan.


=head2 ScanType => Str

The scan type that has been completed.


=head2 StartTime => Str

The time that the resource scan was started.


=head2 Status => Str

Status of the resource scan.

=over

=item IN_PROGRESS

The resource scan is still in progress.

=item COMPLETE

The resource scan is complete.

=item EXPIRED

The resource scan has expired.

=item FAILED

The resource scan has failed.

=back



=head2 StatusReason => Str

The reason for the resource scan status, providing more information if
a failure happened.



